{"tid":949872,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞中國貸款比率「傲視」全港同業　兩年前數據早揭面對風險首當其衝","createTime":"2018-12-21T06:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T04:14:30.000Z","uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8680195c409211fd66261b324d6f70b987decd2","tid":949872,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"2016-6-2 19:02<br />\n去年因中國業務拖累而導致增長放緩的東亞銀行今宣佈裁員，令人憂慮本地銀行業會否被預言「呈L型發展」的中國經濟拖跨。其實，直至2010年很少香港銀行向中國企業批出貸款，但在2013年本地銀行對中國企業大開水喉，貸出總共4,500億美元，佔本地銀行貸款的總數四成三，等同1.65倍本地生產總值。當中，東亞銀行向中國企業批出的貸款，佔其所有貸款的46%，比例接近一半，也是所有香港銀行最高的。其次的是中國銀行（香港），對中國企業貸款佔總數27%；相比之下恆生銀行則只有10%。<br />\n<br />\n隨著近年本地銀行對中國企業的借貸有增無減，這情況早己引起政府金管局及銀行界人士憂慮，但中國一直能夠維持經濟增長7至8%的水平，政府除了表示密切留意，保持監察外，沒有進一步行動。直至，去年中國經濟硬著陸的論調越炒越熱，製造、零售及服務等各行各業市道越來越差，東亞銀行首當其衡，2014年中國業務不良貸款達至1.32%，較恆生的0.18%高出多倍。<br />\n<br />\n即使東亞在2015年中收緊向中國企業批出貸款，但明顯相關安排為時已晚，2015年中國業務不良貸款升至2.63%，數字增加一倍，中國業務的除稅後淨溢利按年下滑81.2%至港幣 3.47億元，整體除稅後溢利較2014年的減少16.8%。<br />\n<br />\n若果中國經濟真的「呈L型發展」，香港銀行對內地企業批出數以萬億計的貸款未必血本無歸，但只要一定比例撇成壞帳，屆時帶來的影響未必限至裁員。<br />\n<br />\n（撰文：談可易）（圖片來源：蘋果日報）"},{"pid":"94dd3627482f1e405d24c5e070ec3ca409e21a2f","tid":949872,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647d1f519761d975a167391bd60ac3420366e476","tid":949872,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:43:36.000Z","msg":"沙皇都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3d508421723c74fe73157bc626e07b29d95b5b","tid":949872,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"因行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21547cdf502f073c65048eb15413cf1f702f4a7","tid":949872,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647d1f519761d975a167391bd60ac3420366e476","tid":949872,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:43:36.000Z","msg":"沙皇都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"最大股東好似係三井住友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e456472edc9208fb02e8fac57616aab4e0ea3c7","tid":949872,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bad debt"},{"pid":"f90f4d6fcc6fd1e65ec2f6cab84917724dcffad1","tid":949872,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"2015後個啲借貸更加精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點只x亞一間吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f181ea23b1c8dac6fcd47f638bf4f9480e106f8","tid":949872,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f90f4d6fcc6fd1e65ec2f6cab84917724dcffad1","tid":949872,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"2015後個啲借貸更加精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點只x亞一間吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"其他早兩年開始禁低緊個ratio"},{"pid":"893bbdd93c0b3dc012665a925653bd0a97946026","tid":949872,"uid":136249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"其實好多大陸人係香港借完錢就拍下蘿友走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bda406db2ed3fe83a967943299916b2b58f24cf","tid":949872,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T18:43:36.000Z","msg":"19年都黎緊， 中國 東亞仲係咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"